# =============================================================================
# NOTES FOR SETUP
# =============================================================================
# 1. Supabase Setup:
#    - Create a new project at https://supabase.com
#    - Get your URL and anon key from the project settings
#    - Run the migrations from /supabase/migrations
#
# 2. Stripe Setup:
#    - Create a Stripe account and get your API keys
#    - Set up webhooks for ACH events
#    - Configure ACH transfers in your Stripe dashboard
#
# 3. Plaid Setup:
#    - Sign up for Plaid and get your credentials
#    - Configure webhook URL in Plaid dashboard
#    - Set appropriate products for your use case
#
# 4. SendGrid Setup:
#    - Create SendGrid account and verify sender identity
#    - Create email templates for different notifications
#    - Configure domain authentication for better deliverability
#
# 5. Security Considerations:
#    - Use environment-specific values (never commit real keys)
#    - Rotate API keys regularly
#    - Enable 2FA on all external service accounts
#    - Use least-privilege access for all integrations